#. [unit]: type=Dwarvish Steelclad
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/12_The_Underlevels.cfg:857
msgid "Zamak"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/12_The_Underlevels.cfg:901
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/12_The_Underlevels.cfg:947
msgid ""
"When I step on this rune, I feel strange indeed. I feel like I am being "
"pulled somewhere else, but at the same time being held back by an equally "
"powerful force."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Angarthing
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/12_The_Underlevels.cfg:906
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/12_The_Underlevels.cfg:952
msgid ""
"It seems to be some sort of a teleportation device. What's more, the "
"bindings that are preventing it from working seem to be the same ones that "
"bar those sealed gates."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Aragoth
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/12_The_Underlevels.cfg:988
msgid "Our master's ritual must not be interrupted. Stop them!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/12_The_Underlevels.cfg:1003
msgid ""
"Yon doors are big, tightly locked - and, I would imagine, well barricaded. "
"This may take a while."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Aiglondur
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/12_The_Underlevels.cfg:1008
msgid ""
"Go thorough that rubble yonder; see if you can dig up some sort of battering "
"ram."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/12_The_Underlevels.cfg:1014
msgid "One hour later"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Aiglondur
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/12_The_Underlevels.cfg:1019
msgid "OK, the door is about to give. Brace yourselves, everyone."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Karrag
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/12_The_Underlevels.cfg:1038
msgid "No! No! No! Dirtgrubbers must die! The true people must rule all!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Aiglondur
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/12_The_Underlevels.cfg:1043
msgid "The 'true people' speak through our axes. Die, foul lich."
